{"title":"2.6 12款AI产品体验分析","slug":"cgzpoi2qv0rex9qg","summary":"前言 人工智能时代不仅重塑了商业模式，也为用户体验层面带来了深刻的变革。在人机交互和界面 UI 设计上，涌现出前所未有的机遇与挑战。如何善用 AI 的功能特性，创造出更符合人类直觉、更具效率的产品形态和交互方式，成为产品经理和体验设计师们需要深入思考的关键问题。 正如推文所言：“","category":"2. AI-UX体验模式","tags":["PART4️⃣ AI驱动的体验设计方法&模式","2. AI-UX体验模式"],"featured":false,"order":62,"level":2,"updatedAt":"2025-08-03","wordCount":2468,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/cgzpoi2qv0rex9qg","html":"<h1 data-lake-id=\"CKhY7\" id=\"CKhY7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3084ce5c\" id=\"u3084ce5c\">前言</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u54cc83e2\" id=\"u54cc83e2\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc953304b\" id=\"uc953304b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">人工智能时代不仅重塑了商业模式，也为用户体验层面带来了深刻的变革。在人机交互和界面 UI 设计上，涌现出前所未有的机遇与挑战。如何善用 AI 的功能特性，创造出更符合人类直觉、更具效率的产品形态和交互方式，成为产品经理和体验设计师们需要深入思考的关键问题。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ua32a0ced\" id=\"ua32a0ced\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc4759a55\" id=\"uc4759a55\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">正如推文所言：“AI-native UX What do apps look like when you design AI first? Starting a thread to collect some examples I've found.”，以下列举的 12 个 AI 产品形态，正是对这一趋势的有力印证，值得我们深入研究和借鉴。</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"Dvla6\" id=\"Dvla6\" data-lake-index-type=\"2\"><span data-lake-id=\"uafc7bd98\" id=\"uafc7bd98\">granola.ai</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"ue707cff6\" id=\"ue707cff6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u675da926\" id=\"u675da926\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Granola. Ai 采用了典型的对话式交互，每一次用户操作都能得到即时的、类人化的信息反馈，这有效地增强了用户与系统之间的信任感和交互透明度。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u6396308f\" id=\"u6396308f\"><span data-lake-id=\"udb911887\" id=\"udb911887\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"background-color: #FBDE28\">设计思考：</span><span data-lake-id=\"ub5c6a85a\" id=\"ub5c6a85a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">这种流畅自然的对话式体验，让用户感觉是在与一个智能助手沟通，而非冷冰冰的机器。对于需要用户逐步完成复杂任务的产品来说，清晰的反馈机制至关重要，Granola. Ai 的实践提供了一个很好的范例。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2e603859\" id=\"u2e603859\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1743339937271-d736d67d-340e-4772-a185-cc9ec2357285.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u73b09e47-8d3b-483c-8ba2-e3586a7aac7%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u19e90326-88cb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A640%2C%22originHeight%22%3A303%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fafafa%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uaca9a3e3%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1f6bdbc6\" id=\"u1f6bdbc6\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1743339937235-0a935862-d8fe-4400-ac16-3e56c567fc7f.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ub8b0d9b0-0466-4a9b-8be2-5a11a3412b5%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u19e90326-88cb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A640%2C%22originHeight%22%3A303%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f9f9f9%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u73f8aef2%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"ykntN\" id=\"ykntN\" data-lake-index-type=\"2\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua4151188\" id=\"ua4151188\">attio.com</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"ub2cb371d\" id=\"ub2cb371d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u28f1fccc\" id=\"u28f1fccc\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Attio. Com 最令人称道之处在于，它将强大的大型语言模型（LLMs）巧妙地嵌入到用户熟悉的表格界面中。这种无缝集成实现了细腻而精准的交互体验，用户无需学习新的操作逻辑，即可享受到 AI 带来的便利。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub1e51117\" id=\"ub1e51117\"><span data-lake-id=\"uec444a3e\" id=\"uec444a3e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"background-color: #FBDE28\">设计思考：</span><span data-lake-id=\"u38c4071b\" id=\"u38c4071b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Attio. Com 展示了 AI 如何与现有工作流融合，而非颠覆它。这种“润物细无声”的设计思路，能有效降低用户的学习成本，让 AI 功能真正融入日常工作之中。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5a38a0ee\" id=\"u5a38a0ee\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1743339937232-bd788783-3dfe-4c0a-9514-1548d575217f.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u4504b4b9-d77c-4da8-ad1b-0a6217c5414%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u19e90326-88cb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A640%2C%22originHeight%22%3A286%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fefefe%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22udff72847%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"n0bbz\" id=\"n0bbz\" data-lake-index-type=\"2\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc3438d15\" id=\"uc3438d15\">rabbitholes.ai</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"ub0df9874\" id=\"ub0df9874\"><span data-lake-id=\"udc3e807a\" id=\"udc3e807a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Rabbitholes. Ai 采用了清晰直观的流程式交互，将复杂任务拆解为一系列易于理解的步骤。其逻辑清晰，引导明确，操作体验流畅自然，即使是初次使用的用户也能快速上手。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud880b371\" id=\"ud880b371\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9dc3c1ce\" id=\"u9dc3c1ce\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"background-color: #FBDE28\">设计思考：</span><span data-lake-id=\"ua562bc1c\" id=\"ua562bc1c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">对于涉及多步骤操作或需要用户输入多项信息的功能，结构化的流程是降低认知负担的关键。Rabbitholes. Ai 的实践表明，良好的流程设计能够显著提升用户体验。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ua7270f2a\" id=\"ua7270f2a\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1743339937307-3327694f-4155-458c-b842-4aa90d5392a2.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u6ec5885b-57cc-4d08-903f-2c00c0172e4%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u19e90326-88cb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A640%2C%22originHeight%22%3A401%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%238b938d%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ue418609a%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u38f4b669\" id=\"u38f4b669\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1743339937245-e2a5d8a9-b393-437d-8f99-328bc29d8b25.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u4c4c9222-8929-4adf-a828-1646cc11449%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u19e90326-88cb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A640%2C%22originHeight%22%3A401%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23121213%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22udc1aa219%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u9aff7d88\" id=\"u9aff7d88\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1743339938039-af68d892-b94c-43b8-8bd0-fb23ab85de6b.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ua5c1013e-e968-436d-8e19-5553c2bf27e%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u19e90326-88cb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A640%2C%22originHeight%22%3A401%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2397a59a%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uddc2fb7b%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"wPL45\" id=\"wPL45\" data-lake-index-type=\"2\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua4eb9cec\" id=\"ua4eb9cec\">tldraw.com</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u67f96e72\" id=\"u67f96e72\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc4fd99be\" id=\"uc4fd99be\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Tldraw. Com 的交互方式非常直观，高度贴合人类的思维模式。正如其描述：“In tldraw computer, you create workflows of connected components that generate and propagate data. Components can take any other components as input. Instructions are written in natural language, letting you work with data in loose, weird, and unexpected ways.” （在 tldraw computer 中，你可以创建连接组件的工作流来生成和传播数据。组件可以将任何其他组件作为输入。指令以自然语言书写，让你以宽松、奇特和意想不到的方式处理数据。）</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1ded44b2\" id=\"u1ded44b2\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc43e9848\" id=\"uc43e9848\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"background-color: #FBDE28\">设计思考：</span><span data-lake-id=\"ube8cd32d\" id=\"ube8cd32d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Tldraw. Com 探索了以自然语言作为交互方式的可能性，这代表着人机交互的未来趋势。它启示我们，AI 可以让用户以更符合直觉的方式与计算机进行沟通。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u33f0ac59\" id=\"u33f0ac59\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1743339938024-98a1e02b-963f-42a6-8a2a-fdc8905eada2.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u3809c7f2-600e-47b0-ab29-ee298e36c81%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u19e90326-88cb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A902%2C%22originHeight%22%3A508%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23eff0f2%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u90f28520%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"zWcsL\" id=\"zWcsL\" data-lake-index-type=\"2\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6cbd3ab7\" id=\"u6cbd3ab7\">herostuff.com</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"ued2deba7\" id=\"ued2deba7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3ad8485a\" id=\"u3ad8485a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Herostuff. Com 巧妙地将现实世界的物品与虚拟平台的交易流程相结合：用户通过 App 扫描实物产品，AI 即可快速识别并预估其转售价值，自动生成商品标题、价格和描述，甚至支持视频录制上传，极大地简化了二手物品的交易流程。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf0ac8d9a\" id=\"uf0ac8d9a\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubcd73e94\" id=\"ubcd73e94\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"background-color: #FBDE28\">设计思考：</span><span data-lake-id=\"ua8868540\" id=\"ua8868540\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Herostuff. Com 的创新之处在于打破了线上线下的界限，利用 AI 将物理世界的操作无缝融入数字体验之中。这种设计思路为 O 2 O 场景下的产品创新提供了新的灵感。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u37fc7891\" id=\"u37fc7891\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1743339938039-5b927694-64be-4e46-9d83-f88a797012ee.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u28e9277a-9e5c-43cb-bb04-927f61fa5ab%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u19e90326-88cb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A640%2C%22originHeight%22%3A440%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%230f1015%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ue315094c%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u9c8f30b1\" id=\"u9c8f30b1\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1743339938165-9ee8ab4d-fda8-431f-8101-46c70c358c9b.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u2383c388-2364-4d