22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"nq0NI\" id=\"nq0NI\" data-lake-index-type=\"2\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5d1b5ccb\" id=\"u5d1b5ccb\">midday.ai</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u69f3cde2\" id=\"u69f3cde2\"><span data-lake-id=\"u69cf12cb\" id=\"u69cf12cb\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">正如其描述：“I think these kinds of &quot;hidden AI features&quot; are really powerful. </span><span data-lake-id=\"uef97aac2\" id=\"uef97aac2\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">🔍</span><span data-lake-id=\"u92359213\" id=\"u92359213\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"> And a combination of all Uses Vercel AI SDK with readStreamableValue.” （我认为这种“隐藏的 AI 功能”非常强大。</span><span data-lake-id=\"u702850ab\" id=\"u702850ab\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">🔍</span><span data-lake-id=\"u90ab842c\" id=\"u90ab842c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"> 并且结合了所有使用 Vercel AI SDK 和 readStreamableValue 的功能。）</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u91f61d6f\" id=\"u91f61d6f\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf567a7f1\" id=\"uf567a7f1\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Midday. Ai 将强大的数据分析能力隐藏在简洁的用户界面之下。用户无需复杂的操作，即可快速获得所需的数据洞察。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1033ae34\" id=\"u1033ae34\"><span data-lake-id=\"u10af4a7b\" id=\"u10af4a7b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"background-color: #FBDE28\">设计思考：</span><span data-lake-id=\"uec842436\" id=\"uec842436\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Midday. Ai 强调了“少即是多”的设计理念。在 AI 时代，将复杂的功能隐藏在简洁的界面背后，让用户专注于核心任务，是一种值得借鉴的设计策略。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf1220e6a\" id=\"uf1220e6a\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1743339946873-70342a54-1388-4b30-a565-dc00ac0d1397.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ub1f88e18-97ef-401c-bb0a-48c3a1b17f5%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u19e90326-88cb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A640%2C%22originHeight%22%3A435%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2310100e%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uc1cd4788%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"pKHdK\" id=\"pKHdK\" data-lake-index-type=\"2\"><span data-lake-id=\"udef10362\" id=\"udef10362\">shapecalendar.com</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"udcd99b3c\" id=\"udcd99b3c\"><span data-lake-id=\"uda620a67\" id=\"uda620a67\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">正如其描述：“Planning workouts with LLMs that has your workout history feels like cheating.” （使用了解你锻炼历史的 LLM 规划锻炼计划感觉就像作弊。）</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u67e177fc\" id=\"u67e177fc\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2235167b\" id=\"u2235167b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Shapecalendar. Com 与传统的社交健身应用不同，它专注于利用 AI 根据用户的个人锻炼历史和目标，智能制定个性化的健身计划。这种智能化的辅助功能，为健身爱好者提供了更精准的指导。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf86ae482\" id=\"uf86ae482\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubbb6d19b\" id=\"ubbb6d19b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"background-color: #FBDE28\">设计思考：</span><span data-lake-id=\"ub9beac66\" id=\"ub9beac66\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">Shapecalendar. Com 展示了 AI 如何实现真正的个性化体验。通过理解用户的历史数据和偏好，AI 可以提供更贴合用户需求的定制化服务，这在提升用户粘性和满意度方面具有重要意义。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u32537997\" id=\"u32537997\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1743339946874-0b1a532e-60fa-4c25-86e6-5b5b8a89b6e5.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ua9524c6e-24ce-40dc-a77f-aded2196879%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u19e90326-88cb-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A640%2C%22originHeight%22%3A549%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23111111%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uea8caae4%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u3f8ac8b1\" id=\"u3f8ac8b1\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9a747944\" id=\"u9a747944\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">​</span><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5dd7a33e\" id=\"u5dd7a33e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u422bc8b2\" id=\"u422bc8b2\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">参考链接：</span><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/DSb14Jp2oN-nl-JvrI72NA\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u3c2908dc\" id=\"u3c2908dc\"><span data-lake-id=\"uafc49fe0\" id=\"uafc49fe0\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/DSb14Jp2oN-nl-JvrI72NA</span></a></p>"}
